Implementation
- Project has two classes and one main driver class

- First class is "CalculatorWidget" class which is responsible from only view part.
Just exposes some methods to manipulate the views and binds inputs from controller to actions

- Second class is "CalculatorController", main logic is implemented in here. 
Just exposes start() method which starts the application, shows the view.

Other methods are responsible from the magic logic of the calculator
such as when digit clicked, currentText is updated.
